properties.areaDesc: Coastal waters from Fernandina Beach to St. Augustine FL out 20 NM
properties.headline: Marine Weather Statement issued January 16 at 8:22AM EST by NWS Jacksonville FL
properties.description:
Patchy to areas of fog will continue to impact portions of the
nearshore coastal waters mainly between Fernandina Beach and Ponte
Vedra Beach and out to 5 to 10 nm, including some estuaries and
some waterways. Local visibilities of around 1 mile or less will
be possible.

Mariners who approach areas of fog are urged to reduce speed, and
keep a lookout for other vessels, buoys, and breakwaters. Keep
your navigation lights on.

NWSheadline: PATCHY DENSE FOG ALONG THE COAST
